## Get specific media_entry
GET {{baseUrl}}/media_entries/{{mediaEntryId}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":200,"msg":"Request success","data":{"id":1,"id_franchise":1,"media_type":"manga","title":"Frieren: Beyond Journey's End","author":"Kanehito Yamada","volumes":13,"episodes":null},"timestamp":"2026-03-15 02:41:14"}


