## Create media_entry — admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/media_entries
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "id_franchise": 4,
    "media_type": "manga",
    "title": "Bocchi the Rock! Special Edition",
    "author": "Aki Hamaji",
    "volumes": 8
}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":201,"msg":"MediaEntry created successfully","data":{"id":14},"timestamp":"2026-03-15 02:41:43"}
### Response (get created media_entry)
// {"status":"success","code":200,"msg":"Request success","data":{"id":14,"id_franchise":4,"media_type":"manga","title":"Bocchi the Rock! Special Edition","author":"Aki Hamaji","volumes":8,"episodes":null},"timestamp":"2026-03-15 02:42:05"}


