## Update media_entry — admin
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/media_entries/{{mediaEntryId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "volumes": 14,
    "author": "Kanehito Yamada"
}

### Response
// {"status":"success","code":200,"msg":"MediaEntry updated successfully","data":null,"timestamp":"2026-03-15 02:42:49"}
### Response (get updated media_entry)
// {"status":"success","code":200,"msg":"Request success","data":{"id":1,"id_franchise":1,"media_type":"manga","title":"Frieren: Beyond Journey's End","author":"Kanehito Yamada","volumes":14,"episodes":null},"timestamp":"2026-03-15 02:43:06"}


## Update — Fail (not found)
